♪ It's just the way
you're looking at me ♪

1:26:28.957 --> 1:26:30.417
♪ Starlight ♪

1:26:30.519 --> 1:26:32.793
♪ Oh, starlight ♪

1:26:32.895 --> 1:26:34.355
♪ Starlight ♪

1:26:34.457 --> 1:26:36.727
♪ Oh, starlight ♪

1:26:36.829 --> 1:26:42.601
♪ I see your green eyes roam
when I'm at your door ♪

1:26:43.301 --> 1:26:45.571
♪ Starlight... ♪

1:26:47.373 --> 1:26:48.669
JUNE:
What are you doing?

