It's a good day,
it's a good day,

1:36:08.497 --> 1:36:11.665
because the sun's shining
and the birds...

1:36:11.767 --> 1:36:15.176
-It's a good day. I told you.
-They saying it's only weeks.

1:36:15.278 --> 1:36:16.577
(both crying)

1:36:16.679 --> 1:36:19.009
JENNIFER:
Oh, I'm so happy for us.

1:36:19.111 --> 1:36:22.242
Oh, June,
it's been 11 years of hell.

1:36:22.344 --> 1:36:23.880
