whichever clothes

1:36:23.982 --> 1:36:25.986
you'd like to wear out of here.

1:36:26.851 --> 1:36:28.620
Maybe some jeans?

1:36:28.722 --> 1:36:30.820
BOTH:
Maybe skirts.

1:36:30.922 --> 1:36:32.788
GLORIA:
Sweetheart,

1:36:33.224 --> 1:36:34.793
you need to take care
of yourself

1:36:34.895 --> 1:36:36.931
